199
00:14:36,953 --> 00:14:39,953
The last week of Lent,

200
00:14:39,953 --> 00:14:42,911
a newborn baby to cry out, walks away ?

201
00:14:42,911 --> 00:14:46,911
a quarter, a three-quarter, a hryvnia.

202
00:14:46,911 --> 00:14:49,912
