217
00:15:46,372 --> 00:15:49,122
Well, mistress or kept woman, whatever you like.

218
00:15:49,122 --> 00:15:51,831
He's at the penitentiary, she's waiting for him,

219
00:15:51,831 --> 00:15:54,831
