224
00:16:11,415 --> 00:16:14,415
Now.

225
00:16:18,582 --> 00:16:21,165
Princess!

226
00:16:21,165 --> 00:16:21,665
Come here!

227
00:16:22,832 --> 00:16:25,832
Come here!

228
00:16:28,749 --> 00:16:30,999
Well, hello, Princess.

229
00:16:30,999 --> 00:16:33,249
And good luck to you, too.

230
00:16:33,249 --> 00:16:35,666
Have a seat.

