247
00:17:23,168 --> 00:17:25,210
We can help clean out your pockets.

248
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:28,210
No, really, I mean, I'm like,

249
00:17:28,627 --> 00:17:31,627
I want to know,

250
00:17:32,877 --> 00:17:35,877
