251
00:17:38,604 --> 00:17:40,604
(Music playing)

252
00:17:49,002 --> 00:17:52,003
Why?

253
00:17:53,169 --> 00:17:56,586
It's not gonna work out,
what do you two have in common?

254
00:17:56,794 --> 00:17:58,378
That's what this is all about.

255
00:17:58,378 --> 00:18:00,920
In the play, I play a drunk.

256
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:06,378
And I, by all means,
I need to catch a glimpse of the real him.

257
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:11,420
Listen to this.

258
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:20,920
The man pays for everything himself.

259
00:18:21,254 --> 00:18:24,254
To faith, to unbelief, to intelligence. To love.

260
00:18:24,962 --> 00:18:26,671
That's why he's free.

261
00:18:26,671 --> 00:18:28,879
Here, what is a human being?

262
