00:22:37,764 --> 00:22:40,765
or whatever they're supposed to do.

321
00:22:41,598 --> 00:22:44,598
Here Fedot look, here.

322
00:22:45,848 --> 00:22:47,348
Vladimir Alexeyevich.

323
00:22:47,348 --> 00:22:50,057
you're the one who pulled me out of pleasant company.

324
00:22:50,057 --> 00:22:51,557
What's the rush?

325
00:22:51,557 --> 00:22:52,848
Well, a dead body.

326
00:22:52,848 --> 00:22:55,473
if I'd waited a couple or three
hours, I don't think he'd go anywhere.

327
00:22:56,979 --> 00:22:58,979
(parrot squawking)

328
00:23:00,307 --> 00:23:02,265
Aha!
