00:24:02,018 --> 00:24:02,976
it's not gone,

352
00:24:02,976 --> 00:24:05,976
it's a hell of a mess.

353
00:24:06,101 --> 00:24:07,476
Lots of goodness.

354
00:24:07,476 --> 00:24:09,435
What if it's someone he knows?

355
00:24:09,435 --> 00:24:11,268
Maybe he let him in.

356
00:24:11,268 --> 00:24:12,768
I mean, who do you know who he knows?

357
00:24:15,602 --> 00:24:18,602
And you, do you know many of his acquaintances?

358
00:24:20,685 --> 00:24:22,685
Yeah, I guess no one.

359
00:24:22,685 --> 00:24:25,186
Uh-huh.
So here I am, nobody but you.

360
00:24:25,186 --> 00:24:28,186
You told me yourself, about your chess games.

361
00:24:29,227 --> 00:24:31,144
Maybe you killed him.

362
00:24:31,144 --> 00:24:33,811
Because of a lost chess game.

363
00:24:33,811 --> 00:24:36,228
(Rudnikov) Well, confess, did you kill?

364
00:24:36,228 --> 00:24:38,311
(Gilyarovsky) Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha. Funny!

365
00:24:38,311 --> 00:24:40,228
(Rudnikoff) Yeah, it's funny.

366
00:24:40,228 --> 00:24:43,228
Gentlemen, there's another dart here.

367
00:24:44,186 --> 00:24:47,186
Just don't touch it with your hands.

368
00:24:49,353 --> 00:24:52,270
Why here?

369
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:52,645
Why,

370
00:24:52,645 --> 00:24:55,645
Why.

371
00:24:56,145 --> 00:24:57,562
The killer missed.

