436
00:28:42,488 --> 00:28:45,488
Do you think you could kill a man with that?

437
00:28:52,780 --> 00:28:55,780
Depends on what the stuff is impregnated with.

438
00:28:56,864 --> 00:28:59,864
(Gilyarovsky) And?
I need time.

439
00:29:00,322 --> 00:29:03,322
(Gilyarovsky) A day...
Two, three,

440
00:29:03,697 --> 00:29:07,197
But no guarantees.
